    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "Geometric patterns are etched into the smooth brown and gray surface of a *staff of earth*, which makes a solid thud whenever tapped against the ground. While wielding a *staff of* earth, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your Fortitude saves and DC against effects that Shove you or knock you prone.",
